_sText:
Update to zm_cell_games_b. It is no longer possible for 40 players to spawn next to each other in small area. Instead, spawn points are now spread across 4 different locations across the map. Now supports 52 players. Added 9 new barricades/holdout spots. All of the map can now be utilized by players at all times. 

Map offers approximately:
12 barricades,3 super barricades,16 holdouts/hideouts.
About 50% of the above is secret or not obvious to set up.
